Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr 10
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that you're a freelance journalist does that mean you're going to write an article about the things we've been talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually when you do write your article please be sure to emphasize this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The moral development of a child all depends on the adult that raises him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is essential that we encourage every child to follow the proper path
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do they'll be able to achieve their dreams and have a happy life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams huh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey diet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A soccer ball
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a soccer ball
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for dinner I was hoping we could continue our conversation another time of course I am sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we couldn't finish it up tonight Mr 10
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I can come by tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well did
